Package com.zello.sdk

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Events
    The Events interface provides a means to intercept key changes within the Zello SDK.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppState
    The AppState class is a representation of the current state of the Zello for Work app at any given moment.
    Audio
    The Audio class acts as an intermediary between the devices audio and the Zello for Work app.
    Contact
    The Contact class acts as a representation of a contact for the user.
    Contacts
    The Contacts class represents the Contacts that the authenticated user has.
    MessageIn
    The MessageIn class represents an incoming message to the Zello for Work app.
    MessageOut
    The MessageOut class represents an outgoing message through the Zello for Work app.
    Zello
    The Zello singleton acts as the primary point of interacting to the Zello SDK.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AudioMode
    The AudioMode enum is a representation of the different mediums for audio output while using the Zello SDK.
    ContactStatus
    The ContactStatus enum represents the status of a Contact.
    ContactType
    The ContactType enum represents the type of Contact.
    Error
    The Error enum represents some of the authentication errors that can be encountered in the Zello SDK.
    State
    The State enum represents the authentication state of the user.
    Status
    The Status enum represents the status of a Contact.
    Tab
    The Tab enum represents the UI Tabs of the Zello for Work app.
    Theme
    The Theme enum represents the UI themes available using the Zello SDK.
